Megatron:





Megatron stepped to KitKat's other side. He stared out into the 
darkness, sneering. "I'm going out there. But I will need 
reinforcements. KitKat and Terrorsaur shall go with me." He turned 
his head and called: "Terrorsaur!" 

The flier turned his attention to him and jogged to him. 

"I want you to fly out and tell us what you see." he said.

Terrorsaur nodded and took to the air.
